<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>St Francis Girls Suwerwa High school</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/high.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../layout/header-full', { navActive: 'home' }) %>

<!-- HERO SLIDESHOW -->
<section class="hero-slider" id="heroSlider">
  <div class="slide active">
    <div class="slide-bg" style="background-image:url('https://www.sfgsuwerwa.sc.ke/images/bg/moi-high-school-ab.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="slide-content">
      <p class="eyebrow fade-up">Welcome to SFG SUWERWA</p>
      <h1 class="fade-up delay-1">On Earth<br><span>We Rise!</span></h1>
      <p class="fade-up delay-2">A public secondary school providing holistic Christian-based quality education for the service of God and mankind.</p>
      <div class="fade-up delay-3">
        <a href="profile.html" class="btn-gold">Learn More</a>
        <a href="apply.html" class="btn-outline">Apply Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-bg"></div>
    <div class="slide-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Vision</p>
      <h1>A Christian School<br><span>of Choice</span></h1>
      <p>We strive to be the premier institution anchoring all endeavors on the fear of the Lord and enduring Christian values.</p>
      <div>
        <a href="mvv.html" class="btn-gold">Our Vision</a>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-bg"></div>
    <div class="slide-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Academic Excellence</p>
      <h1>Shaping <span>Future</span><br>Leaders</h1>
      <p>Consistently top-performing in KCSE, our rigorous academic programme prepares students for success in higher education and beyond.</p>
      <div>
        <a href="kcse.html" class="btn-gold">KCSE Results</a>
        <a href="gallery.html" class="btn-outline">Gallery</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <button class="slider-arrow prev" id="prevSlide"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></button>
  <button class="slider-arrow next" id="nextSlide"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></button>

  <div class="slider-nav">
    <span class="slider-dot active" data-slide="0"></span>
    <span class="slider-dot" data-slide="1"></span>
    <span class="slider-dot" data-slide="2"></span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VISION / MISSION / VALUES -->
<section class="vmv-strip">
  <p class="section-label">Our Foundation</p>
  <h2>Vision, Mission &amp; Core Values</h2>
  <div class="vmv-grid">
    <div class="vmv-card">
      <div class="vmv-icon"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div>
      <h3>Our Vision</h3>
      <p>To be a Christian School of Choice  a beacon of academic and moral excellence in Kenya and beyond.</p>
      <a href="mvv.html" class="read-more-link">Read More</a>
    </div>
    <div class="vmv-card">
      <div class="vmv-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>To provide holistic educational services in a learner-centered, co-educational Christian set-up guided by commitment, fairness and integrity.</p>
      <a href="mvv.html" class="read-more-link">Read More</a>
    </div>
    <div class="vmv-card">
      <div class="vmv-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
      <h3>Core Values</h3>
      <p><strong>Commitment</strong>  to excellence in all we do.<br><strong>Fairness</strong>  treating all with dignity.<br><strong>Integrity</strong>  honesty and accountability always.</p>
      <a href="mvv.html" class="read-more-link">Read More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MOTTO BANNER -->
<div class="motto-banner">
  <h3>Our Motto</h3>
  <h2>On Earth We Rise!</h2>
  <p>One of Kenya's most prestigious schools, recognised for sustained academic excellence and holistic development of students.</p>
  <a href="contact.html">Contact Us Today</a>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT + APPLICATIONS -->
<div class="about-section">
  <div class="about-text">
    <p class="section-label">Who We Are</p>
    <h2>Welcome to St Francis Girls Suwerwa</h2>
    <p>St Francis Girls Suwerwa is a top-performing school located in Trans Nzoia County, Kenya. The school is well-known for its academic and co-curricular excellence, offering a vibrant, stimulating learning environment that prioritises the holistic development of students.</p>
    <p>The school provides a rigorous academic programme that prepares students for success in higher education and beyond, with a highly qualified teaching staff who use modern techniques to make learning engaging, interactive, and memorable.</p>
    <p>With a well-established library, well-equipped classrooms, and modern facilities, students at SFG Suwerwa are assured of quality learning experiences.</p>
    <a href="profile.html" class="read-more">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="font-size: 11px;"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class="applications-box">
      <span class="badge">Now Open</span>
      <h3>Applications Invited</h3>
      <p>Admissions for the upcoming academic year are now open. Join Kenya's premier Christian secondary school and unlock your full potential.</p>
      <a href="apply.html">How to Apply </a>
      <div class="divider-light">
        <p class="app-list-item"><i class="fas fa-calendar icon-gold-margin"></i> View Term Dates</p>
        <p class="app-list-item"><i class="fas fa-money-bill icon-gold-margin"></i> Fee Payment Info</p>
        <p class="app-list-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle icon-gold-margin"></i> Admission Criteria</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NOTICE BOARD -->
<section class="notice-section">
  <p class="section-label">Latest Updates</p>
  <h2>School Notice Board</h2>
  <div class="notice-grid">
    <div class="notice-card">
      <div class="notice-img">
        <img src="https://www.sfgsuwerwa.sc.ke/images/speasyimagegallery/albums/1/images/moi-senior-school.jpeg" alt="Moi Senior School Kabarak"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.innerHTML='<i class=\'fas fa-school notice-img-placeholder\'></i>'">
      </div>
      <div class="notice-body">
        <p class="notice-date"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt icon-margin"></i> 04 December 2025</p>
        <h3>Moi Senior School  Kabarak</h3>
        <p>Our mission: to provide holistic educational services in a learner-centred, co-educational Christian environment guided by excellence in all undertakings.</p>
        <a href="noticeboard.html">Read More </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="notice-card">
      <div class="notice-img">
        <img src="https://www.sfgsuwerwa.sc.ke/images/gallery/term-dates.png" alt="2025 Term Dates"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.innerHTML='<i class=\'fas fa-calendar notice-img-placeholder\'></i>'">
      </div>
      <div class="notice-body">
        <p class="notice-date"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt icon-margin"></i> 04 June 2025</p>
        <h3>2025 Term Dates</h3>
        <p>The 2025 academic year calendar is now available. Opening date for the first term was 6th January 2025.</p>
        <a href="terms.html">Read More </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="notice-card">
      <div class="notice-img notice-img-custom">
        <i class="fas fa-newspaper notice-icon"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="notice-body">
        <p class="notice-date"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt icon-margin"></i> 2026</p>
        <h3>School Magazine 2026</h3>
        <p>The latest edition of the SFG Suwerwa school magazine is now available for download.</p>
        <a href="https://www.sfgsuwerwa.sc.ke/images/documents/SFG Suwerwa_magazine_2026.pdf" target="_blank">Download PDF </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="center-link">
    <a href="noticeboard.html">View All Notices</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EMBODIMENT OF HOPE -->
<section class="embodiment">
  <div class="embodiment-img">
    <div class="embodiment-img-inner">
      <i class="fas fa-cross cross-icon"></i>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="embodiment-content">
    <p class="section-label">Our Foundation</p>
    <h2>Embodiment of <span>Hope</span></h2>
    <p>St Francis Girls Suwerwa anchors all its endeavors on the fear of the Lord and Christian values. The Board of Directors, the school administration, the staff, students and all stakeholders put God first in their day-to-day activities.</p>
    <p>The exceptionally outstanding performance that the school has posted for years on end can be attributed to committed, highly-trained staff, as well as disciplined and focused students. We give glory and honour to God Almighty for this achievement.</p>
    <a href="profile.html" class="btn-gold">Learn More</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><h3>50+</h3><p>Years of Excellence</p></div>
  <div class="stat"><h3>A</h3><p>KCSE Mean Grade</p></div>
  <div class="stat"><h3>40+</h3><p>Clubs &amp; Societies</p></div>
  <div class="stat"><h3>100%</h3><p>Christian Values</p></div>
</div>

<!-- PARTNERS -->
<section class="partners">
  <p class="section-label">Our Community</p>
  <h2>Partner Institutions</h2>
  <div class="partner-logos">
    <div class="partner-logo">SFG<br>Suwerwa</div>
    <div class="partner-logo">suwerwa<br>University</div>
    <div class="partner-logo">Ministry of<br>Education</div>
    <div class="partner-logo"><br></div>
    <div class="partner-logo"><br></div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('../layout/footer') %>
<%- include('../layout/search-overlay') %>
</body>
</html>
